      <head>Carl von Klobassa</head>
      <div>

        <p>Pupil of Heinrich Schenker.</p>

        <p>Dr. Carl von Klobassa took lessons with Schenker during the year 1906/07. In June 1907,
          he was dilatory in settling up his fees for the year, and Schenker had to threaten legal
          action (diary, May 1907) in order to force him to pay up. Klobassa failed to turn up at
          the beginning of the teaching year 1907/08 (diary, October 1, 1907).</p>
      </div>
